Title: Early Works
Actors: Milja Vujanovic, Bogdan Tirnanic, Cedomir Radovic, Marko Nikolic
Plot: Inspired by Karl Marx's "Das Kapital", three men and a girl named Jugoslava decide to wake up the conscience within the working class and peasants. Faced with the primitivism and a lack of morale, their revolution fails and the girl is one to be sacrificed as a witness of their unsuccessful attempt.
